| date= 10 October 1957
| place = Windscale, [[Seascale]], [[Cumbria]] (now [[Sellafield]])
| outcome = [[International Nuclear Event Scale|INES]] Level 5 (accident with wider consequences)
| coordinates = {{coord|54.4243|N|3.4982|W|region:GB_type:landmark|display=inline,title}}
|reported injuries = Estimated 240 additional cases of [[thyroid cancer]]
